    Acceleration in a nonlinear harmonic oscillator with:
      - linear and nonlinear (cubic, quartic) stiffness,
      - linear and nonlinear (cubic, quartic) damping,
      - mixed polynomial interaction terms,
      - sinusoidal forcing depending on position and velocity,
      - cross sinusoidal interaction terms.

    Parameters:
    - x0 (np.ndarray): Position at time t.
    - x1 (np.ndarray): Velocity at time t.
    - params (np.ndarray): Array of 12 trainable coefficients.

