        + params[12] * (x0**2) * (x1**2)   # quadratic-quadratic cross term
        
        + params[13] * (x0**3) * (x1**2)   # cubic-quadratic cross term
        
        + params[14] * (x0**2) * (x1**3)   # quadratic-cubic cross term
